OL,3,CCut national insurance and hike income
OL,4,Ctax to meet fiscal rules, think tank
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FRachel Reeves should cut national
OL,8,Finsurance and increase income tax to
OL,9,Fcreate a "level playing field" and
OL,10,Fprotect workers' pay, a think tank has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FIn a report published on Tuesday, the
OL,14,FResolution Foundation said the
OL,15,FChancellor should send a "decisive
OL,16,Fsignal" that she will take "tough
OL,17,Fdecisions" on tax to calm jittery bond
OL,18,Fmarkets.
