OL,3,CCut national insurance and hike income
OL,4,Ctax to meet fiscal rules, think tank
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt comes as Ms Reeves prepares to
OL,8,Fdeliver a Budget in November that is
OL,9,Fwidely expected to see significant tax
OL,10,Frises as she battles to meet her
OL,11,Ffiscal rules.
OL,13,FAmong the tax changes proposed by the
OL,14,FResolution Foundation was a 2p cut in
OL,15,Fnational insurance, matched by a 2p
OL,16,Frise in income tax.
