OL,3,CCut national insurance and hike income
OL,4,Ctax to meet fiscal rules, think tank
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe think tank argued that the switch
OL,8,Fwould raise #6 billion and help tackle
OL,9,F"unfairness" in the tax system, as
OL,10,Fincome tax is paid by more people
OL,11,Fincluding pensioners and landlords.
OL,13,FBut the change would provide only some
OL,14,Fof the #20 billion of tax rises the
OL,15,Fthink tank estimated would be needed
OL,16,Fby 2029/30 thanks to a combination of
OL,17,Fincreased borrowing costs, lacklustre
OL,18,Fgrowth and new spending commitments.
