OL,3,CCut national insurance and hike income
OL,4,Ctax to meet fiscal rules, think tank
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAdam Corlett, principal economist at
OL,8,Fthe Resolution Foundation, said
OL,9,Fcutting national insurance and
OL,10,Fincreasing income tax "should form
OL,11,Fpart of wider efforts to level the
OL,12,Fplaying field on tax".
OL,14,FOther proposals put forward by the
OL,15,Fthink tank include increasing the tax
OL,16,Fon dividends, addressing a "worrying"
OL,17,Fgrowth in unpaid corporation tax from
OL,18,Fsmall businesses, applying a carbon
OL,19,Fcharge to long-haul flights and
OL,20,Fshipping, and expanding taxation of
OL,21,Fsugar and salt.
