OL,3,CCut national insurance and hike income
OL,4,Ctax to meet fiscal rules, think tank
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt also proposed gradually reducing
OL,8,Fthe threshold at which businesses pay
OL,9,FVAT from #90,000 to #30,000, saying
OL,10,Fthis would help "promote fair
OL,11,Fcompetition" and raise #2 billion a
OL,12,Fyear by 2029/30.
OL,14,FMr Corlett said: "Policy U-turns,
OL,15,Fhigher borrowing costs and lower
OL,16,Fproductivity growth mean that the
OL,17,FChancellor will need to act to avoid
OL,18,Fborrowing costs rising even further
OL,19,Fthis autumn.
