OL,3,CCut national insurance and hike income
OL,4,Ctax to meet fiscal rules, think tank
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"Significant tax rises will be needed
OL,8,Ffor the Chancellor to send a clear
OL,9,Fsignal that the UK's public finances
OL,10,Fare under control.
OL,12,F"Any tax rises are likely to be
OL,13,Fpainful but given the fallout from the
OL,14,Frecent employer NI rise, the
OL,15,FChancellor should do all she can to
OL,16,Favoid loading further pain onto
OL,17,Fworkers' pay packets."
