OL,3,CCut national insurance and hike income
OL,4,Ctax to meet fiscal rules, think tank
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Government has repeatedly insisted
OL,8,Fthat it will keep its manifesto
OL,9,Fpromise not to raise income tax,
OL,10,Fnational insurance or VAT.
OL,12,FBut the Chancellor will face a
OL,13,Fdifficult balancing act when she
OL,14,Fdelivers her Budget on November 26 in
OL,15,Ftrying to meet that pledge while also
OL,16,Fsticking to the rules she has set
OL,17,Fherself on borrowing.
