OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FWhile the Resolution Foundation
OL,8,Festimated Ms Reeves would need to
OL,9,Fraise taxes by #20 billion, others
OL,10,Fhave suggested the figure could be as
OL,11,Fhigh as #51 billion.
OL,13,FA Treasury spokesperson said: "The
OL,14,FChancellor makes tax policy decisions
OL,15,Fat fiscal events. We do not comment on
OL,16,Fspeculation around future changes to
OL,17,Ftax policy."
